author: stefan2
msg: Speed up the metadata check for log. addressed FSFS repos.
* subversion/libsvn_fs_fs/cached_data.c
(svn_fs_fs__check_rep): Reuse the rev / pack file through the same
hinting mechanism as in older formats.

author: stefan2
msg: Make 'svnadmin verify --metadata-only' for FSFS f7 not only cover all
rev / pack file data but also the revprops.
In contrast to the rev / pack file checks, this will not detect all
possible modifications but it guarantees that no revprops are missing
or corrupted in a way that checkout etc. would fail.
* subversion/libsvn_fs_fs/verify.c
(verify_revprops): New verfication sub-function.
(verify_index_consistency): Rename this ...
(verify_f7_metadata_consistency): ... to that.  Call the new function
as well.
(svn_fs_fs__verify): Update caller.
